                  <rs id="t18500819-1393-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18500819-1393-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="miscellaneous"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18500819-1393-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="returnFromTransportation"></interp>, feloniously being at large before the expiration of the term for which he had been transported.</rs>
